ProMA - ProFTPd MySQL Admin
===========================
$Id$

ABOUT
-----
ProMA is a PHP4 based system for administrating a ProFTPd server
storing users in a MySQL database.


CREDITS
-------
ProMA is written entirely by Stein Magnus Jodal (stein.magnus@jodal.no).
I would also like to give some credits to all the people behind
ProFTPd, mod_sql and MySQL for their effort for the Open Source community.


REQUIREMENTS
------------
- Webserver, with
- PHP4, with
- MySQL support
- ProFTPd server with mod_sql and mod_sql_mysql 4.xx configured
  to find users in a
- MySQL database


CHANGES
-------
Read 'ChangeLog' for details on changes since last release.


